<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTA78">
<l>tuṇaināṭ peruṅkiḷaiyun tolkulamuñ cuṟṟat</l>
<l>tiṇaināḷu miṉpuṭaittā mēluṅ kaṇaināṇi</l>
<l>lōvāt toḻilcārṅkaṉ ṟolcīrai naṉṉeñcē</l>
<l>yōvāta vūṇāka vuṇ.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Even if we were to have companions, days, many relatives,</l>
<l>an old family, the aid of a retinue and daily pleasures, absorb,</l>
<l>as unceasing food, good heart, the ancient excellence of the Cārṅka bearer</l>
<l>whose work does not cease, with arrows on the string.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
